name: Steve Fox
bio: Steve Fox is a world-renowned boxing champion known for his speed, precision, and evasive movement. He was born as part of a genetic experiment under the Mishima Zaibatsu and later escaped to pursue a life of his own. Steve fights using pure boxing techniques — he has no kicks — relying instead on fast punches, sways, ducks, and powerful counters. His unique movement stances make him one of the most technical characters in Tekken.
